!! Wiki assistant chat

Chat mode with wiki overview injected into the system prompt (`inject-as: system-prompt`). The LLM knows the wiki structure and can use tools to dig deeper.

''Settings covered:'' chat mode, `output-mode: text`, `output-target: display`, `inject-as: system-prompt`, widget attribute precedence, tools enabled

```
<$llm-chat
  chatTiddler="$:/temp/rimir/llm-connect/examples/wiki-assistant-chat"
  systemPrompt="You are a helpful TiddlyWiki assistant."
  tools="[tag[$:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/tool]]"
  contextTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/context-templates/wiki-overview"
/>
```

